data.description: PRICED TO SELL! Stunning and well taken care of Luxury Series Model home in the much desired Park West Subdivision.  3 Car Garage. Back yard view and a premium size lot. Open floor plan. Neutral colors throughout. Granite counter tops. Under cabinet lighting. Ceiling fans and blinds throughout. Spacious pantry and lots of cabinet space. This property is a great space for entertaining. It is a must see!!
